    "By 2022, this number had grown to over 5.5 million.",
    "The amount of deleted content has also been growing, but at a much slower rate.",
    "In 2013, there were approximately 500,000 articles deleted from Wikipedia.",
    "By 2022, this number had grown to over 1 million.",
    "That is, over 60% of new articles are deleted."
